metadata.description:
**Lurk's Mutant Colony** 

 The mutants have evolved and are multiplying over Pluton. These uniquely generated Lurkons have been derived directly from the MAYC ecosystem and carry Lurkâ€™s unique characteristic trippy style. Each Lurkon has the ability to spawn offspring to create larger colonies of mutants that will fight over dominion of the territories of Pluton. Bounties abound for those who manage to capture dominion over each territory.
